    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    Push Video Wallpaper Key uses advanced rendering technology that places video playback directly onto the desktop background layer of Windows. Unlike running videos in a media player window, this program integrates with the Windows Explorer shell to replace the static desktop wallpaper with a video layer. The software creates a transparent overlay that sits behind all desktop icons but above the desktop background, allowing videos to play seamlessly while you continue working with full access to your files and applications .
    
    🔹 VIDEO PLAYBACK ENGINE
    The program utilizes a high-performance video player engine with the following capabilities:
    
    • HARDWARE ACCELERATION: GPU-based decoding for smooth playback with minimal CPU usage (typically 1-5% CPU)
    • DIRECTX INTEGRATION: DirectX 11/12 rendering for optimal performance
    • VIDEO FORMAT SUPPORT: MP4, AVI, MKV, MOV, WEBM, GIF, and 50+ other formats
    • RESOLUTION HANDLING: Automatically scales videos to fit any screen resolution up to 8K
    • FRAME RATE CONTROL: Adaptive frame rate matching to monitor refresh rate (60Hz, 144Hz, 240Hz)
    • LOOPING OPTIONS: Continuous loop, play once, or playlist rotation
    
    🔹 AUDIO MANAGEMENT
